{"tid":913601,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[屍體派對] 而家呢個年代仲有無人會玩恐怖rpg game?","createTime":"2018-11-23T13:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T02:27:01.000Z","uid":52658,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"828fd7445482a7cbd70e940466f6cc33ab90e868","tid":913601,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/daDKbhI9A-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdaDKbhI9A-E&d=XETi2Bt%2BZpnTLEalwkJRlgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8c1de3a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/daDKbhI9A-E</a><br />\n<br />\n前幾日無意發現<br />\n見佢d畫風幾靚所以禁入去睇下佢咩料<br />\n點知一睇就上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再睇埋佢個動畫版<br />\n睇到三十幾集 夜媽媽睇真係好心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好恐怖<br />\n想問呢度有無人有玩過呢隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n刻命裕也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n篠崎直美呢條八婆真係好撚柒煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e3e9843df7af67ae7d4dc12a40ed44ac0fe62e","tid":913601,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3370d90e15b8737cf579c6b35bcd7773e666c136","tid":913601,"uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e7e3e9843df7af67ae7d4dc12a40ed44ac0fe62e","tid":913601,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"躝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上個post比人屌唔撚夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"c46bb58b24dd4846a252a5cc496ccfda0b53aac9","tid":913601,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d24047c5398bba1fc8eb3c4f09bcdf2b3e399ea3","t